<h2 id="chord-progressions">Chord progressions</h2>

<h3 id="intro--instrumental-breaks">Intro &amp; instrumental breaks</h3>

<p>During the instrumental breaks (played with solos), they repeat this same progression many times.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>G C D D
C D G G
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="chorus">Chorus:</h3>

<p>Note, only in the 2nd chorus, the second-to-last chord is a ‚ÄúC‚Äù before resolving to the final ‚ÄúG‚Äù.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>"I'd like to settle down but they won't let me..."

G C D D
C C D D
G C D D
C D G G
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="verse">Verse</h3>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>"Well, I raised a lot of Cain back in my younger days..."

G C D D
C C D D
G C D D
C C D D
</code></pre></div></div>
